reviewText: These are decent recording of exactly what they say they are.  HOWEVER,  they are NOT all region.  This means they will not play on the standard player that can be purchased in the US.  They must be played on a DVD player that has all region capability.  I was fortunate enough to have such a player, but didn't expect to need it.  DO NOT BUY UNLESS YOU HAVE AN ALL REGION PLAYER.
